1486 void BulletObject::TimeOutQuant(void)
1487 {
1488  int d;
1489  uchar alt;
1490  Vector v;
1491  VangerFunctionType* g;
1492 
1493  if(TargetObject){
1494  v = Vector(getDistX(TargetObject->R_curr.x,R_curr.x),getDistY(TargetObject->R_curr.y,R_curr.y),TargetObject->R_curr.z - R_curr.z);
1495  if((TargetObject->Status & SOBJ_DISCONNECT) || (TargetObject->ID == ID_VANGER && (!((VangerUnit*)(TargetObject))->ExternalDraw || ((VangerUnit*)(TargetObject))->draw_mode != NORMAL_DRAW_MODE || ((VangerUnit*)(TargetObject))->BeebonationFlag)))
1496  TargetObject = NULL;
1497  };
1498 
1499  if(BulletMode & BULLET_CONTROL_MODE::TARGET){
1500  switch(TargetMode){
1501  case BULLET_TARGET_MODE::CONTROL:
1502  if(TargetObject) vTarget = v;
1503  else{
1504  vTarget = Vector(0,0,0);
1505  BulletMode &= ~BULLET_CONTROL_MODE::TARGET;
1506  };
1507  break;
1508  case BULLET_TARGET_MODE::LEFT_ROUND:
1509  vTarget = Vector(vDelta.y,-vDelta.x,0);
1510  break;
1511  case BULLET_TARGET_MODE::RIGHT_ROUND:
1512  vTarget = Vector(-vDelta.y,vDelta.x,0);
1513  break;
1514  case BULLET_TARGET_MODE::RANDOM:
1515  if(RND(100) < 10) vTarget = Vector(BMAX_TARGET_VECTOR - RND(BMAX_TARGET_VECTOR2),BMAX_TARGET_VECTOR - RND(BMAX_TARGET_VECTOR2),BMAX_TARGET_VECTOR - RND(BMAX_TARGET_VECTOR2));
1516  break;
1517  case BULLET_TARGET_MODE::WALL:
1518  v.x = getDistX(R_curr.x,vWallTarget.x);
1519  v.y = getDistY(R_curr.y,vWallTarget.y);
1520  vTarget.x = v.x - v.y;
1521  vTarget.y = v.y + v.x;
1522  vTarget.z = 0;
1523  break;
1524  };
1525 
1526  d = vTarget.vabs();
1527  if(d){
1528  vDelta += vTarget * Precision / d;
1529  d = vDelta.vabs();
1530  if(d > Speed) vDelta = vDelta * Speed / d;
1531  };
1532  };
1533 
1534  vTail = R_curr;
1535  R_curr += vDelta;
1536  cycleTor(R_curr.x,R_curr.y);
1537 
1538  Time--;
1539  Power -= DeltaPower;
1540 
1541  if(Visibility == VISIBLE){
1542  g = ActD.fTail;
1543  while(g){
1544  if(g->ID == PROTRACTOR_PALLADIUM){
1545  v = Vector(getDistX(R_curr.x,g->vR.x),getDistY(R_curr.y,g->vR.y),0);
1546  d = v.vabs();
1547  if(d < PALLADIUM_RADIUS){
1548  vDelta = Vector(Speed,0,0)*DBM(PI/2 + v.psi(),Z_AXIS);
1549  R_curr = vTail;
1550  R_curr += vDelta;
1551  cycleTor(R_curr.x,R_curr.y);
1552  };
1553  break;
1554  };
1555  g = g->Next;
1556  };
1557 
1558  if(Time <= 0)
1559  Event(BULLET_EVENT_ID::LIFE_TIME_DESTROY);
1560 
1561  if(BulletMode & BULLET_CONTROL_MODE::FLY){
1562  v = vTail;
1563  if(MapLineTrace(v,R_curr)){
1564  R_curr = v;
1565  Event(BULLET_EVENT_ID::MAP_DESTROY);
1566  };
1567  }else{
1568  if(ShowID == BULLET_SHOW_TYPE_ID::CRATER && ExtShowType){
1569  if(BigGetAlt(R_curr.x,R_curr.y,R_curr.z,alt,ExtShowType)) MapLevel = 1;
1570  else{
1571  MapLevel = 0;
1572  alt = 0;
1573  if(LightData){
1574  LightData->Destroy();
1575  LightData = NULL;
1576  };
1577  };
1578  }else MapLevel = GetAlt(R_curr.x,R_curr.y,R_curr.z,alt);
1579  R_curr.z = alt + AltOffset;
1580  };
1581  }else{
1582  if(Time <= 0)
1583  Event(BULLET_EVENT_ID::HIDE_LIFE_TIME_DESTROY);
1584  };
1585 
1586 // if(ShowID == BULLET_SHOW_TYPE_ID::PARTICLE){
1587 // EffD.CreateParticle(ExtShowType,vTail,R_curr,ShowType);
1588 // if(BulletScale)
1589 // EffD.CreateParticle(ExtShowType,vTail,R_curr,ShowType);
1590 // };
